txt.en: Ally to the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl
The Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl now know to call upon you in times of strife, and many among them consider you a trusted ally to the City of the Corsairs.
You must earn Ally standing with the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl
You are now considered a trusted ally by many of the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl.
